query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('2007',
'csom',
'designer-workflow',
'india',
'infopath',
'jquery',
'permissions',
'rest',
'sharepoint-addin')
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 1 AND u1.upvotes <= 100
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('money',
'sharepoint') group by t1.name;
